      "message": "The current implementation will also work.\nBut we could have done it better by putting ExecutorService here and starting multiple FileClientHandler to listen for files.\nIn current approach, we are creating a fileWatcherThread which then creates multiple threads using ExecutorService. So the current flow is DistributionMainThread -> fileWatcherThread -> ExecutorService(with inline run method)\n\nWith my suggestion the flow will be DistributionMainThread -> ExecutorService(FileClientHandler)",
